45:54.605 --> 45:55.605
Cinaglia.

45:56.765 --> 45:57.765
Come over here.

46:03.565 --> 46:04.965
Well?

46:05.045 --> 46:06.965
In the end you were right, huh?

46:07.605 --> 46:09.205
You made just one mistake.

46:11.245 --> 46:13.165
You needed Samurai's help again.

46:14.285 --> 46:15.885
We started out together.

46:23.325 --> 46:24.325
To this city.

46:31.845 --> 46:33.885
Now we're on the same side.

46:34.485 --> 46:37.085
I'm not interested one bit
in your business.

46:37.165 --> 46:38.325
What are you interested in?

46:39.845 --> 46:40.685
Immigrants.

46:40.765 --> 46:42.365
That's a good business, too.

46:42.925 --> 46:45.085
I can put my properties at your disposal.

46:47.725 --> 46:48.725
We can go.

46:49.245 --> 46:50.565
No, not yet.

46:52.205 --> 46:54.565
We have to set the terms of the deal.

46:56.045 --> 46:57.965
I want Adami and the Anacletis gone.

46:58.565 --> 46:59.965
How can I get rid of them?

47:00.045 --> 47:01.965
They're the ones who did everything.

47:02.045 --> 47:04.525
Now that you've won,
you don't need them anymore.

47:07.725 --> 47:09.725
Give him some ideas
on how to save his ass.

47:09.805 --> 47:11.325
I think he needs them.

47:19.445 --> 47:21.005
We'll find a solution.

